      "raw_text": "OF the many manufacturing enter\nprises of Spokane there are none\nin touch with the dear public, both at\nhome and abroad than the flour mill\ning industry. This city is well sup\npiled in this particular, too, or will\nbe when the Centennial mills, which\nwere destroyed by fire nearly year\nago, and which are now in process of\nreconstruction, are completed.\n\n\nThere are four Touring mills in\nSpokane, with an aggregate capacity\nof over half a million barrels of flour\nper year. They are the c. & G. mills.\ndaily capacity coo barrels; Echo mills."
